Text: Shares of NASDAQ DVY traded down $1.30 during midday trading on Tuesday, reaching $101.07. 410,573 shares of the company were exchanged, compared to its average volume of 607,479. iShares Select Dividend ETF has a one year low of $84.62 and a one year high of $103.78.
